Name: Advanced Bike Components
Strength: Component specialists, especially their innovative shocks and drive system.

Name: Affordable Sports Equipment
Overview: Purchase bike components in bulk and assemble their own bikes.
Strength: Very reasonable costs for mid-price bikes.

Name: Another Bicycle Company
Overview: Major road bike and touring bike dealer. They have a complete line of accessories and parts.
Strength: Large stock and variety of parts; they carry almost everything.

Name: Certified Bicycle Supply
Overview: A well-known mountain and touring bike dealer. They are aggressively marketing in the West.
Strength: Well-known in the mid-west, and expanding. They compete head on with the Mountain-300.

Name: Coalition Bike Company
Overview: Produce family oriented bikes. Competes with our lower end.
Strength: Carried by major sports warehouse chains. Tough competition.

Name: Engineered Bike Systems
Overview: Primary focus is BMX and mountain bikes.
Strength: Strong customer loyalty. People move up with them - get BMX as kids, and move on to the mountain bikes.

Name: Initial Bike Company
Overview: One of our top 5 competitors for touring bikes. This is their only focus.
Strength: They were 2nd in the industry in mountain bike sales last year; strong name recognition.

Name: Kickstand Sellers
Overview: An east-coast company that specializes in road bikes, scooters, and tandems.
Strength: They have a specialty niche in tandems; sell lots of road bikes too.

Name: Metro Bike Works
Overview: Competes with our lower end bikes, all lines.
Strength: Mountain bikes are their top seller; they do a large volume.

Name: On-line Bike Sellers
Overview: Strong presence on the web; focus on high end road bikes.
Strength: Creative internet marketing. Solid products with all disk brakes.

Name: Only Bikes and Accessories
Strength: Regional service centers are well-like; used as distribution points too.

Name: Orange Bicycle Company
Overview: Manufacture mountain bikes. They sell through both dealers and direct sales.
Strength: They have one of the best team riders in the industry. Suspension forks are superior.

Name: The Gear Store
Strength: Dominate the light-frame market; titanium frames.

Name: Unified Sports Company
Overview: Produce all types of bikes and frames. International sales force.

Name: Widget Bicycle Specialists
Overview: Mid-size manufacturer/dealer for mountain and comfort bikes for all price ranges.
Strength: New models look tough in single-track competition. Very light-weight frame.
